# Borrow validation

Roots, joins, move safety and facts.

## Contract

- Input: validated HIR, external package metadata and access rules
- Output: read-only side-table facts
- Decides: exclusivity, alias safety, inferred-move safety, advisory drop sites
- Must not decide: HIR shape, backend lowering, final ownership
- Invariant: borrow validation reads HIR and writes side tables: it doesn't rewrite HIR

## Main paths

- `src/compiler_frontend/analysis/borrow_checker/`

